## HashMap.keys() method

Returns a new Iterator object that contains the keys for each element in the hash map in insertion order.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
keys(): IterableIterator<K>;
```
<b>Returns:</b>

IterableIterator&lt;K&gt;
